government%20contractors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20always%20get%20a%20huge%20influx%20of%20interest%20in%20our%20services%20when%20there%20are%20mass%20layoffs%20%E2%80%94%20like%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-layoffs-job-cuts-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-layoffs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20recently%20started%20getting%20calls%20from%20job%20seekers%20in%20the%20federal%20sector.%20In%20February%2C%20I%20shared%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Ferinkennedycprw_to-all-the-laid-off-federal-employees-activity-7298761799510675456-DBBU%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%26rcm%3DACoAADUBHZkBkQtfgXGHioQ4drLkJgMnLmVK56o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%20telling%20laid-off%20federal%20workers%20about%20our%20services%20which%20led%20to%20increased%20interest%20in%20our%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20two%20private%20companies%20that%20are%20government%20contractors%20have%20asked%20us%20to%20rewrite%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20for%20their%20employees%20because%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-doge-early-spending-dei-contracts-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtracts%20have%20been%20terminated%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20aren't%20up%20for%20renewal.%20Another%20company%20asked%20us%20to%20do%20a%20webinar%20about%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9-writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20at%20a%20contractor%20company%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20normal.%26quot%3B%20They're%20experiencing%20sudden%20chaos%20and%20want%20to%20be%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c7b6d47-ac97-4072-a6c9-79d3198d3fd2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20federal%20workers%20are%20looking%20to%20switch%20to%20the%20private%20sector%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20contacted%20by%20federal%20employees%20who've%20been%20laid%20off%20and%20those%20who%20are%20still%20employed%20but%20are%20looking%20to%20leave%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20spoken%20to%20federal%20employees%20who%20say%20they%20received%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-workers-react-frustration-fear-doge-productivity-email-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE's%20email%3C%2Fa%3E%20requesting%20their%20accomplishments%20for%20the%20week.%20They%20reached%20out%20to%20me%20because%20they're%20unsure%20about%20the%20future%20of%20federal%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20employee%20who%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20tell%20their%20staff%20about%20how%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20email%20reached%20out.%20She%20said%20it's%20total%20chaos.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20still%20employed%20but%20said%20she%20and%20some%20of%20her%20colleagues%20are%20looking%20to%20leave%20the%20federal%20sector.%20She%20said%20everyone%20is%20on%20edge%20and%20feels%20like%20their%20employment%20may%20be%20terminated%20at%20any%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20spoken%20to%20dozens%20of%20employees%20who%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-workers-private-sector-job-search-challenge-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswitch%20from%20federal%20to%20corporate%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20unusual%20because%20federal%20employees%20we%20work%20with%20typically%20want%20another%20federal%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a926f4b6-6e85-4658-a5eb-8c55b32637d8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20my%20top%20job%20seeking%20tips%20for%20federal%20employees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20transitioning%20out%20of%20a%20federal%20career%2C%20I'd%20advise%20removing%20things%20like%20a%20veteran%20preference%20statement%2C%20citizenship%20status%2C%20salary%2C%20and%20the%20hours%20you've%20worked%20from%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20can%20be%20required%20on%20a%20federal%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20want%20them%20on%20a%20corporate%20one.%20Divulging%20too%20much%20personal%20information%20may%20expose%20you%20to%20bias%2C%20unconscious%20or%20otherwise.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20notice%20a%20lot%20of%20federal%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20list%20every%20course%20the%20person%20has%20taken%20in%20college%2C%20but%20you%20need%20your%20degree.%20I've%20also%20noticed%20federal%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20including%20objective%20statements%2C%20a%20sentence%20focusing%20on%20what%20kind%20of%20role%20you%20want.%20However%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20better%20to%20include%20a%20career%20summary%20%E2%80%94%20a%20paragraph%20that%20highlights%20your%20skillset%20and%20what%20you%20bring%20to%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20advise%20employees%20who%20have%20been%20laid%20off%20to%20say%20on%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20the%20company%20downsized%2C%20hence%20the%20layoffs.%20For%20laid-off%20federal%20workers%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20widespread%20cuts%20is%20enough.%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20should%20go%20into%20the%20whole%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20are%20scared%20about%20losing%20their%20jobs%2C%20my%20first%20piece%20of%20advice%20is%20to%20think%20about%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%20next.%20Ask%20yourself%20if%20you%20like%20your%20role%20and%20if%20you%20want%20your%20next%20job%20to%20be%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20also%20encourage%20you%20to%20start%20using%20LinkedIn.%20Comment%20and%20engage%20with%20other%20people's%20posts%2C%20like%20the%20pages%20of%20companies%20you%20want%20to%20work%20for%20and%20connect%20with%20people%20who%20work%20at%20those%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20developed%20a%20relationship%20with%20contacts%20at%20a%20company%2C%20you%20can%20say%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20role%20and%20ask%20about%20openings.%20Warming%20up%20your%20network%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20you%20still%20need%20to%20have%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20ready.%20If%20someone%20does%20reach%20out%20to%20you%20about%20an%20opportunity%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20they're%20probably%20going%20to%20ask%20for%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20Or%2C%20if%20someone%20has%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20looks%20you%20up%20on%20LinkedIn%20but%20sees%20your%20profile%20is%20really%20sparse%20and%20lacking%20detail%2C%20that's%20not%20helping%20them%20either.%20You%20can't%20have%20one%20without%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinding-job-awful-right-now-drop-in-openings-tough-search-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20job%20market's%3C%2Fa%3E%20especially%20competitive%20right%20now%2C%20so%20all%20of%20this%20couldn't%20have%20happened%20at%20a%20worse%20time.%20We're%20just%20trying%20to%20help%20as%20many%20people%20as%20we%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EResponding%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20a%20representative%20from%20the%20White%20House%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20returned%20to%20Washington%20with%20a%20mandate%20from%20the%20American%20people%20to%20bring%20about%20unprecedented%20change%20in%20our%20federal%20government%20to%20uproot%20waste%2C%20fraud%2C%20and%20abuse.%20This%20isn't%20easy%20to%20do%20in%20a%20broken%20system%20entrenched%20in%20bureaucracy%20and%20bloat%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20task%20long%20overdue.%20The%20personal%20financial%20situation%20of%20every%20American%20is%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20the%20President%2C%20which%20is%20why%20he's%20working%20to%20cut%20regulations%2C%20reshore%20jobs%2C%20lower%20taxes%2C%20and%20make%20government%20more%20efficient.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Accheong%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eccheong%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20charissacheong.95%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUse%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20here's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-tips-federal-workers-switching-career-private-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742552301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dbf2e3b8b41a9673fb2fab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-tips-federal-workers-switching-career-private-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Government%20employees%20are%20panicked%20and%20want%20to%20switch%20to%20corporate%20jobs%2C%20said%20Erin%20Kennedy%2C%20CEO%20of%20Professional%20Resume%20Services%2C%20Inc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ccheong%40insider.com%20(Charissa%20Cheong)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-tips-federal-workers-switching-career-private-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DP%20World%2C%20Reliance%20Industries%20join%20hands%20for%20innovative%20rail%20solution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742552282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdp-world-reliance-industries-join-hands-for-innovative-rail-solution-125032100585_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20reducing%20over%20700%20km%20of%20road%20transport%20per%20container%2C%20the%20rail%20solution%20significantly%20reduces%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20contributes%20to%20Reliance's%20environmental%20goals%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdp-world-reliance-industries-join-hands-for-innovative-rail-solution-125032100585_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What%20RSS'%20Calls%20For%20'Moderation'%20Really%20Tell%20Us%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20%C2%A0Sangh%20(RSS)%20is%20celebrating%20100%20years%20since%20its%20inception%E2%80%94a%20remarkable%20journey%20for%20an%20organisation%20that%20was%20long%20considered%20untouchable%20and%20ridiculed%20by%20the%20intellectual%20class%20yet%20has%20not%20only%20survived%2C%20but%20thrived.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20with%20its%20glorious%20legacy%20of%20members%20like%20Gandhi%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Patel%2C%20Tilak%2C%20and%20Bose%2C%20has%20fractured%20multiple%20times%3B%20the%20Socialists%E2%80%94once%20led%20by%20JP%20and%20Lohia%E2%80%94have%20become%20almost%20unrecognisable%2C%20splintering%20so%20often%20that%20their%20divisions%20are%20beyond%20count%3B%20even%20the%20Communists%20have%20seen%20splits%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20proliferation%20of%20leftist%20parties.%20The%20RSS%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20has%20had%20none%20of%20this.%20Even%20though%20it%20is%20not%20an%20intellectual%20movement%2C%20it%20has%20successfully%20developed%20a%20process%E2%80%94driven%20by%20patience%20and%20resilience%E2%80%94that%20has%20propelled%20it%20as%20a%20hegemonic%20force.%20If%20the%20Congress%20fails%20to%20course-correct%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20surprise%20if%20the%2021st%20century%20is%20seen%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20RSS%20and%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeeping%20Up%20With%20The%20Times%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20has%20a%20remarkable%20ability%20to%20adapt%20to%20changing%20circumstances%20without%20losing%20its%20ideological%20foundation.%20Sure%2C%20it%20may%20have%20withdrawn%20certain%20chapters%20of%20Bunch%20of%20Thoughts%20or%20moderated%20some%20of%20Golwalkar's%20statements%2C%20but%20it%20has%20never%20compromised%20on%20its%20core%20ideology.%20After%20Gandhi's%20assassination%20and%20in%20the%20towering%20presence%20of%20Nehru%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20RSS%E2%80%94operating%20through%20the%20Jan%20Sangh%20and%20later%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%94avoided%20overt%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric%2C%20instead%20engaging%20in%20the%20constitutional%20and%20parliamentary%20process.%20However%2C%20after%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20passing%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20ascent%2C%20the%20RSS%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20openly%20advance%20Hindutva%20through%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20movement.%20It%20sidelined%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20elevating%20hardliner%20LK%20Advani%20as%20the%20face%20of%20its%20agenda.%20Later%2C%20when%20coalition%20politics%20demanded%20a%20more%20moderate%20stance%2C%20Vajpayee%20was%20brought%20back%2C%20eventually%20serving%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202013%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20deeply%20discredited%20and%20the%20conditions%20ripe%20for%20Hindutva's%20resurgence%2C%20the%20RSS%20preferred%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20lead%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%2010%20years%20have%20been%20particularly%20fertile%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20Hindutva.%20The%20strength%20of%20the%20RSS%20should%20not%20be%20measured%20by%20the%20number%20of%20states%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%2C%20the%20offices%20and%20buildings%20it%20has%20constructed%2C%20or%20the%20growth%20of%20its%20shakhas%20and%20new%20members.%20Instead%2C%20its%20true%20strength%20is%20reflected%20in%20how%20widely%20the%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%20has%20been%20accepted%20by%20a%20significant%20section%20of%20Hindus.%20Electoral%20victories%20and%20physical%20expansion%20are%20merely%20superficial%20indicators%20of%20success%E2%80%94temporary%20in%20nature.%20What%20is%20more%20fundamental%20and%20enduring%20is%20the%20exponential%20rise%20in%20Hindu%20consciousness%20and%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHindu%20Consciousness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20has%20successfully%20dismantled%20the%20earlier%20hesitation%20among%20Hindus%20towards%20openly%20embracing%20their%20identity.%20Not%20too%20long%20ago%2C%20many%20Hindus%20were%20reluctant%20to%20wear%20their%20religious%20identity%20on%20their%20sleeves%2C%20fearing%20that%20doing%20so%20would%20lead%20to%20accusations%20of%20communalism%20and%20a%20significant%20perception%20loss.%20The%20socio-political%20ecosystem%20was%20dominated%20by%20left-liberal%20thought%2C%20which%20discouraged%20overt%20religious%20identities.%20Religion%20was%20confined%20to%20the%20private%20sphere%2C%20and%20it%20was%20widely%20preached%20and%20practised%20that%20India%2C%20as%20a%20secular%20state%2C%20must%20maintain%20a%20clear%20separation%20between%20religion%20and%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Under%20the%20state's%20patronage%2C%20Hindu%20identity%20is%20worn%20more%20aggressively%20than%20ever%2C%20with%20competitive%20displays%20common.%20While%20a%20majority%20of%20upper-caste%20Hindus%20are%20fully%20aligned%20with%20Hindutva%2C%20sections%20of%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits%20have%20also%20joined%20this%20movement%2C%20shedding%20their%20reservations%20about%20asserting%20their%20Hindu%20identity.%20These%20are%20the%20%E2%80%98New%20Hindus'%E2%80%94a%20group%20whose%20idiom%20and%20language%20differ%20from%20those%20of%20traditional%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20socio-cultural%20metamorphosis%20carries%20an%20inherent%20flaw%2C%20however.%20Its%20foundation%20is%20built%20on%20hatred%20toward%20Muslims%2C%20which%20has%20left%20both%20a%20large%20section%20of%20Hindus%E2%80%94including%20many%20silent%20supporters%20of%20Hindutva%E2%80%94and%20Muslims%20wary%20of%20a%20disruptive%20present%20and%20a%20potentially%20challenging%20future.%20There%20is%20growing%20apprehension%20that%20if%20the%20current%20trajectory%20continues%20unchecked%2C%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20widespread%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Dilemma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20while%20the%20RSS%20takes%20great%20pride%20in%20its%20mission%20to%20unite%20Hindus%20as%20a%20civilisational%20goal%2C%20this%20has%20also%20created%20fissures%20within.%20Hindus%20are%20now%20highly%20polarised.%20The%20aggressive%20rhetoric%20of%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20active%20connivance%20of%20the%20state%20apparatus%2C%20has%20instilled%20fear%20and%20anxiety%20in%20a%20segment%20of%20the%20Hindu%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20that%20the%20RSS%20leadership%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20dangers%20posed%20by%20the%20aggressive%20Hindutva%20embraced%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98New%20Hindus'.%20Since%202018%2C%20statements%20from%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20suggest%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20this%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Nagpur%20Violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20the%20statement%20by%20senior%20RSS%20functionary%20Sunil%20Ambekar%E2%80%94that%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20relevant%20now%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94assumes%20significance.%20He%20further%20remarked%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20any%20type%20of%20violence%20is%20not%20good%20for%20society.%E2%80%9D%20Ambekar%20was%20commenting%20on%20the%20Nagpur%20violence%2C%20which%20was%20triggered%20by%20aggressive%20statements%20from%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20leaders%2C%20who%20demanded%20that%20Aurangzeb's%20tomb%20be%20razed.%20As%20rumours%20spread%2C%20they%20incited%20anger%20among%20sections%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20leading%20to%20stone-pelting%20and%20the%20burning%20of%20public%20property.%20More%20than%2040%20people%2C%20including%20several%20police%20officers%2C%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Ambekar's%20intention%20is%20to%20suggest%20that%20Aurangzeb%20is%20a%20historical%20figure%20of%20the%20past%20and%20that%20there%20is%20no%20merit%20in%20revisiting%20the%20issue%20to%20settle%20scores%20with%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20then%20his%20statement%20is%20a%20welcome%20one.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20Bhagwat%2C%20too%2C%20has%20made%20several%20statements%20that%20seem%20aimed%20at%20softening%20the%20aggressive%20stance%20of%20Hindutva%20warriors.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20made%20a%20particularly%20significant%20remark%3A%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20Muslims%2C%20Hindutva%20is%20incomplete.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20this%20had%20little%20impact%20on%20hardcore%20Hindutva%20proponents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20court%20order%20to%20investigate%20whether%20a%20temple%20once%20existed%20at%20the%20mosque%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20Bhagwat%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20search%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Eshivling%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20every%20mosque%3F%E2%80%9D%20Yet%2C%20soon%20after%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20India%20witnessed%20one%20of%20the%20most%20communal%20poll%20campaigns%20in%20its%20history%2C%20where%20BJP%20stalwarts%20openly%20said%20things%20like%20%E2%80%9Cbatenge%20to%20katenge%E2%80%9D%20(if%20divided%2C%20we'll%20die)%20and%20%E2%80%9Cek%20hain%20to%20safe%20hain%E2%80%9D%20(united%2C%20we%20are%20safe).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20implications%20of%20Sunil%20Ambekar's%20statement%20about%20Aurangzeb.%20One%20could%20argue%20that%20the%20RSS%20has%20been%20riding%20a%20ferocious%20tiger%E2%80%94one%20that%20thrives%20on%20hatred%20for%20Muslims.%20Taming%20it%20is%20no%20easy%20task.%20Yet%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20alter%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20RSS%20genuinely%20committed%20to%20change%3F%20Let%20us%20wait%20and%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20co-founder%20of%C2%A0SatyaHindi.com)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742552100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F4bbeo46g_rss-chief-mohan-bhagwat_160x120_01_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhats-behind-recent-rss-calls-for-moderation-7975981%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20could%20argue%20that%20the%20RSS%20has%20been%20riding%20a%20ferocious%20tiger%2C%20one%20that%20thrives%20on%20hatred%20for%20Muslims.%20There's%20no%20taming%20it%2C%20but%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20alter%20its%20course.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhats-behind-recent-rss-calls-for-moderation-7975981%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20family%20and%20I%20moved%20from%20California%20to%20Italy.%20Living%20here%20has%20made%20me%20a%20better%20mom.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clara%20Hogan%20with%20her%20two%20kids%20at%20a%20cafe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d9eaa4b8b41a9673fb089d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMoving%20to%20Italy%20has%20changed%20the%20way%20we%20live%20for%20the%20better.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Clara%20Hogan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMoving%20to%20Italy%20from%20the%20Bay%20Area%20helped%20me%20become%20a%20calmer%2C%20more%20present%20version%20of%20myself.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli