0was%20no%20escaping%20it.%20We'd%20drive%20to%20school%2C%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20the%20park%2C%20friends'%20houses%2C%20and%20activities%2C%20which%20all%20required%20navigating%20Bay%20Area%20interstates%20and%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20I%20don't%20miss%20driving%20at%20all.%20We%20walk%20everywhere.%20My%20youngest%20rides%20in%20the%20stroller%20or%20walks%20and%20my%20oldest%20zips%20around%20on%20her%20scooter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20healthier%2C%20more%20social%2C%20and%20way%20more%20fun%20than%20sitting%20in%20traffic%20and%20waging%20car%20seat%20battles.%20Walking%20means%20fresh%20air%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20passing%20by%20independent%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20small%20shops%2C%20and%20family-run%20restaurants%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20support%20local%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20racing%20between%20parking%20lots%2C%20we%20see%20where%20our%20walks%20take%20us%20%E2%80%94%20stopping%20for%20an%20espresso%20or%20to%20peek%20into%20a%20bookstore%20%E2%80%94%20turning%20errands%20into%20a%20daily%20rhythm%20of%20connection%20to%20our%20neighbors%20and%20each%20other.%20I%20have%20some%20of%20my%20best%20chats%20with%20my%20kids%20while%20we're%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c38701c2-f6a2-489f-897d-7c7a9c1e74d7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Major%20life%20stressors%20that%20worked%20me%20up%20in%20the%20US%20are%20gone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20California%2C%20day%20care%20costs%20were%20crushing%20%E2%80%94%20totaling%20more%20than%20our%20mortgage.%20Here%2C%20however%2C%20even%20the%20private%20preschool%20we%20chose%20(since%20we%20weren't%20residents%20in%20time%20to%20enroll%20in%20public%20school)%20costs%20about%20one-eighth%20of%20what%20we%20paid%20for%20day%20care%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20meals%3F%20Incredible.%20My%20daughters%20eat%20a%20three-course%20lunch%20every%20day%20prepared%20by%20an%20in-school%20cook%20who%20shops%20at%20the%20local%20market%20each%20mornin