s%20on%20drugs%20that%20were%2080-90%25%20of%20the%20way%20to%20success%20before%20being%20scrapped%20due%20to%20safety%20issues.%20The%20startup%20says%20its%20proprietary%20AI%20platform%20identifies%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20toxicity%20and%20provides%20recommendations%20for%20chemical%20adjustments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWindsor%20said%20the%20last%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20had%20been%20a%20difficult%20fundraising%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20kiss%20a%20lot%20of%20frogs%20along%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20really%20had%20to%20find%20the%20right%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20plans%20to%20use%20the%20fresh%20funding%20to%20acquire%20more%20distressed%20assets%20and%20advance%20its%20first%20drug%2C%20a%20PDE9A%20inhibitor%20for%20treating%20Alzheimer's%2C%20into%20early%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20out%20the%2014-slide%20pitch%20deck%20Ignota%20used%20to%20raise%20its%20seed%20round.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ignota%20p1%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ca16b2585f1dff88b16bed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EIgnota%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alta%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67caa5c5b8b41a9673f9f664%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EIgnota%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ignota%203%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67caa5eeb8b41a9673f9f669%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EIgnota%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3