0citizen%20with%20Palestinian%20roots%2C%20it%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20chapter%20in%20their%20lives.%20It%20was%20an%20%26quot%3BIndo-Palestinian%26quot%3B%20love%20story%2C%20because%20borders%20can't%20limit%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20India%20was%20a%20big%20leap%20for%20Mapheze%20Saleh.%20The%20Gazan%20knew%20India%20as%20the%20land%20of%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20and%20as%20she%20travelled%20to%20Delhi%2C%20her%20friends%20asked%20her%20to%20convey%20their%20greetings%20to%20SRK%20and%20even%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20faces%20of%20Indian%20cinema%20that%20transcended%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20changed%20for%20the%20couple%20when%20they%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20after%20spending%20years%20in%20India.%20The%20first%20big%20change%20came%20in%202023%20with%20the%20Middle%20East%20conflict.%20The%20next%20was%20the%20return%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20early%20this%20year%2C%20which%20marked%20a%20stark%20shift%20in%20the%20US%20policy%20on%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Saleh%20would%20never%20have%20anticipated%20that%20her%20Palestinian%20roots%20would%20pose%20bigger%20challenges%20in%20the%20US.%20US%20academics%20now%20face%20deportation%20if%20they%20demonstrate%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Hamas.%20Mahmoud%20Khalil%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20who%20studied%20at%20Columbia%20University%2C%20was%20arrested%20for%20staging%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrouble%20Begins%20For%20Suri%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrouble%20for%20Mr%20Suri%20began%20on%20March%2017%20night%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%20outside%20his%20Virginia%20home%20by%20masked%20agents%20of%20the%20Homeland%20Security%20Department.%20He%20was%20told%20his%20visa%20had%20been%20revoked%20and%20that%20he%20would%20be%20put%20on%20deportation%20trial%20under%20the%20same%20law%20used%20against%20Khalil%2C%20per%20a%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20his%20lawyer%20seeking%20his%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post-doctoral%20fellow%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20insisted%20he%20never%20had%20a%20criminal%20record%2C%20but%20US%20authorities%20accused%20him%20of%20spreading%20%26quot%3BHamas%20propaganda%26quot%3B%20and%20being%20in%20close%20contact%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuspected%20terrorist%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuri%20was%20a%20foreign%20exchange%20student%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20actively%20spreading%20Hamas%20propaganda%20and%20promoting%20antisemitism%20on%20social%20media.%20Suri%20has%20close%20connections%20to%20a%20known%20or%20suspected%20terrorist%2C%20who%20is%20a%20senior%20advisor%20to%20Hamas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tricia%20McLaughlin%2C%20an%20Assistant%20Secretary%20Department%2C%20Homeland%20Security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%20for%20release%2C%20his%20lawyer%20Hassan%20Ahmad%20denounced%20his%20arrest%20as%20being%20%26quot%3Btargeted%2C%20retaliatory%20detention%26quot%3B%2C%20aimed%20at%20silencing%20those%20expressing%20support%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20Palestinians.%20Mr%20Ahmad%20argued%20Mr%20Suri%20was%20being%20targeted%20due%20to%20his%20wife's%20Palestinian%20roots.%20Due%20to%20her%20Palestinian%20heritage%2C%20the%20government%20suspects%20that%20the%20couple%20opposed%20US%20foreign%20policy%20for%20Israel%2C%20according%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Georgetown%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Suri%20was%20a%20faculty%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20in%20Washington%2C%20where%20he%20has%20been%20teaching%20%26quot%3BMajoritarianism%20and%20Minority%20Rights%20in%20South%20Asia%26quot%3B.%20He%20had%20obtained%20a%20US%20visa%20to%20continue%20his%20%26quot%3Bdoctoral%20research%20on%20peacebuilding%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20a%20university%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20him%20engaging%20in%20any%20illegal%20activity%2C%20and%20we%20have%20not%20received%20a%20reason%20for%20his%20detention.%20We%20support%20our%20community%20members'%20rights%20to%20free%20and%20open%20inquiry%2C%20deliberation%2C%20and%20debate%2C%20even%20if%20the%20underlying%20ideas%20may%20be%20difficult%2C%20controversial%2C%20or%20objectionable.%20We%20expect%20the%20legal%20system%20to%20adjudicate%20this%20case%20fairly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20university%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Alleged%20Hamas%20Link%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Saleh's%20father%2C%20Ahmed%20Yourself%2C%20had%20served%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsenior%20political%20adviser%20to%20Hamas%26quot%3B.%20He%20had%20written%20at%20least%20two%20op-ed%20pieces%20(from%202009%20and%202014)%20for%20The%20Guardian%2C%20in%20which%20he%20spoke%20about%20the%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20piece%20for%20Middle%20East%20Eye%20in%202017%2C%20he%20highlighted%20an%20%26quot%3Bactive%20unwillingness%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20global%20community%20to%20acknowledge%20Hamas's%20efforts%20to%20clarify%20their%20position%20towards%20Israel%20and%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20not%20openly%20linked%20Ms%20Saleh%20or%20her%20father%20to%20Mr%20Suri's%20arrest%2C%20but%20a%20senior%20US%20official%20reacted%20to%20a%20post%20about%20the%20Hamas%20links.%20On%20X%2C%20Ms%20McLaughlin%20criticised%20Politico%20for%20describing%20Mr%20Yousef's%20alleged%20link%20to%20Hamas%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwrinkle%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State%20was%20determined%20to%20determine%20Mr%20Suri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yousef%2C%20a%20former%20adviser%20to%20the%20late%20Hamas%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F03%2F19%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fgeorgetown-suri-detained.html%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20son-in-law%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20any%20political%20activism%2C%20let%20alone%20Hamas.%20Speaking%20to%20another%20outlet%2C%20he%20said%20been%20trying%20to%20contact%20Mr%20Suri%20but%20couldn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20cited%20in%20the%20Politico%20report%2C%20he%20branded%20Mr%20Suri's%20detention%20an%20%26quot%3Babduction%20by%20the%20government%26quot%3B%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20Mahmoud%20Khalil.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20trying%20to%20speak%20with%20him.%20That%20hasn't%20happened%20yet.%20This%20is%20just%20another%20example%20of%20our%20government%20abducting%20people%20the%20same%20way%20they%20abducted%20Khalil%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Yousef.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWife%20Appeals%20For%20Safe%20Return%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Saleh%20was%20born%20in%20Missouri%20and%20had%20moved%20to%20Gaza%20when%20she%20was%20five%20years%20old.%20In%20an%20emergency%20motion%20filing%20with%20the%20American%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20(ACLU)%2C%20a%20civil%20rights%20organisation%2C%20she%20has%20made%20an%20appeal%20for%20her%20husband's%20safe%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20with%20their%20children%20in%202022-23%20due%20to%20its%20reputation%20for%20%26quot%3Bfree%20speech%20and%20religious%20freedom%26quot%3B%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcnewsnow.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Fvirginia%2Farlington-county%2Fi-watched-him-being-driven-away-with-no-idea-why-he-had-been-arrested-wife-of-georgetown-university-scholar-recounts-night-he-was-detained%2F%5C%22%3EDC%20News%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20local%20outlet%20cited%20Ms%20Saleh%20as%20saying.%20Mr%20Suri%20had%20already%20landed%20a%20fellowship%20at%20Georgetown%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20take%20the%20leap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20Middle%20Conflict%20in%20October%202023%2C%20Ms%20Saleh%20turned%20active%20on%20social%20media.%20She%20felt%20she%20was%20obliged%20to%20speak%20out%20due%20to%20her%20journalism%20background%20and%20her%20Palestinian%20heritage.%20She%20posted%20content%20daily%20about%20the%20plight%20of%20Gazans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20she%20first%20learnt%20that%20she%20was%20being%20targeted%20over%20her%20father's%20role%20in%20the%20Gaza%20government%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20her%20social%20media%20posts.%20She%20said%20the%20articles%20about%20her%20and%20her%20family%20made%20her%20feel%20unsafe%2C%20especially%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20claims%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20couple%20had%20links%20to%20Hamas.%20Her%20husband%20was%20arrested%20the%20following%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20provided%20a%20personal%20account%20narrating%20the%20events%20surrounding%20her%20husband's%20arrest.%20Around%209%3A20%20pm%20(local%20time)%20on%20March%2017%2C%20she%20got%20a%20call%20from%20her%20husband.%20He%20told%20her%20that%20he%20was%20being%20arrested%20outside%20their%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Saleh%20said%20she%20came%20downstairs%20to%20find%20three%20uniformed%20agents%20handcuffing%20her%20husband.%20They%20shoved%20him%20into%20a%20black%20SUV%20and%20left%20without%20providing%20a%20reason%20for%20his%20arrest.%20Next%20day%2C%20he%20informed%20her%20he%20was%20in%20Lousiana%2C%20about%201%2C600%20km%20from%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20has%20been%20under%20extreme%20stress%20since%20her%20husband's%20arrest%20and%20feels%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20unsafe%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20stop%20looking%20at%20the%20door%2C%20terrified%20that%20someone%20else%20will%20come%20and%20take%20me%20and%20the%20children%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20authorities%20asserted%20they%20would%20deport%20Mr%20Suri%2C%20a%20local%20court%20this%20morning%20blocked%20his%20immediate%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Suri%20is%20among%20the%20latest%20academics%20to%20face%20Trump's%20fury%20over%20supporting%20Palestine%2C%20whom%20the%20President%20calls%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20sympathizers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20who%20seeks%20to%20be%20a%20global%20peacemaker%2C%20has%20warned%20Hamas%20to%20return%20the%20Israeli%20hostages%20still%20held%20captive%20in%20Gaza.%20He%20has%20also%20backed%20the%20latest%20assault%20by%20Israel%20that%20followed%20the%20end%20of%20weeks-long%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20pro-Palestine%20campus%20protests%2C%20his%20warning%20was%20pointed%20and%20direct.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20US%20President%20had%20threatened%20to%20cut%20university%20funding%20for%20staging%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20protests.%20Those%20participating%20may%20also%20be%20charged%20and%20deported%2C%20he%20had%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742550960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fdrb56sqg_badar-khan-suri-mapheze-salez_625x300_21_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbadar-khan-suri-the-alleged-hamas-link-that-landed-indian-researcher-in-trouble-in-us-7974432%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian%20researcher's%20arrest%20in%20the%20US%20over%20his%20alleged%20ties%20to%20Hamas%20has%20put%20the%20focus%20on%20his%20in-laws%2C%20a%20Palestine-origin%20family%20with%20alleged%20links%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20fighting%20a%20year-long%20war%20with%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbadar-khan-suri-the-alleged-hamas-link-that-landed-indian-researcher-in-trouble-in-us-7974432%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20High%20Court%20Justice%20Yashwant%20Varma%2C%20At%20Centre%20Of%20Cash-In-Home%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjustice-yashwant-varma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustice%20Yashwant%20Varma%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20judge%20who%20finds%20himself%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20controversy%20after%20unaccounted%20cash%20was%20found%20at%20his%20bungalow%20in%20t