day%2C%20President%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20directing%20Education%20Secretary%20Linda%20McMahon%20to%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20shutting%20down%20the%20government%20agency.%20The%20order%20instructs%20Ms%20McMahon%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20all%20necessary%20steps%20to%20facilitate%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20and%20return%20authority%20over%20education%20to%20the%20States%20and%20local%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20fullest%20extent%20permitted%20by%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20a%20major%20shake-up%20of%20the%20American%20education%20system%2C%20has%20been%20a%20Republican%20talking%20point%20for%20decades.%20While%20closing%20the%20department%20outright%20would%20require%20congressional%20action%2C%20Trump's%20administration%20has%20already%20begun%20taking%20steps%20to%20weaken%20its%20influence.%20The%20department's%20workforce%20has%20been%20cut%20in%20half%2C%20its%20research%20arm%2C%20the%20Institute%20of%20Education%20Sciences%2C%20has%20been%20gutted%20while%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk-led%20Department%20Of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE)%20has%20cracked%20down%20on%20several%20contracts%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%201979%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Education%20has%20spent%20over%20%243%20trillion%20with%20virtually%20nothing%20to%20show%20for%20it.%20Despite%20per-pupil%20spending%20having%20increased%20by%20more%20than%20245%20per%20cent%20over%20that%20period%2C%20there%20has%20been%20virtually%20no%20measurable%20improvement%20in%20student%20achievement%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Education%20Department%20distributes%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20federal%20funds%20to%20schools%20and%20universities%2C%20overseeing%20civil%20rights%20protections%2C%20and%20managing%20the%20federal%20student%20loan%20program.%20Trump's%20plan%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20future%20of%20these%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20Trump%20Want%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20and%20his%20allies%20contend%20that%20federal%20oversight%20-%20particularly%20through%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20-has%20failed%20students%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20parents.%20His%20case%20for%20dismantling%20the%20department%20hinges%20on%20a%20familiar%20conservative%20argument%3A%20that%20education%20is%20best%20managed%20at%20the%20state%20and%20local%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Nation's%20bright%20future%20relies%20on%20empowered%20families%2C%20engaged%20communities%2C%20and%20excellent%20educational%20opportunities%20for%20every%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump's%20order%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20wants%20to%20cut%20off%20government%20funding%20to%20schools%20and%20universities%20that%20promote%20what%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20race%20theory%2C%20transgender%20insanity%2C%20and%20other%20inappropriate%20racial%2C%20sexual%2C%20or%20political%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%2045%20years%20the%20United%20States%20spends%20more%20money%20on%20education%20by%20far%20than%20any%20other%20country%20and%20spends%20likewise%20by%20far%20more%20money%20per%20pupil%20than%20any%20country%20and%20it's%20not%20even%20close%20but%20yet%20we%20rank%20near%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20list%20in%20terms%20of%20success.%20We%20are%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20list%20and%20we've%20been%20there%20for%20a%20long%20time.%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20eighth%20graders%20are%20not%20proficient%20in%20either%20reading%20or%20math.%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20fourth%20graders%20lack%20even%20basic%20reading%20skills.%20Our%20Public%20elementary%20and%20middle%20schools%20score%20worse%20in%20reading%20today%20than%20when%20the%20department%20opened%20by%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20%26quot%3Bbottom%20of%20the%20list%26quot%3B%20claim%20was%20fact-checked%20by%20Nat%20Malkus%2C%20senior%20fellow%20and%20the%20deputy%20director%20of%20education%20policy%20at%20the%20conservative-leaning%20American%20Enterprise%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20you%20cut%20it%2C%20the%20US%20is%20not%20scoring%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20international%20rankings.%20The%20US%20ranks%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20pack%20on%20most%20international%20assessments%2C%26quot%3B%20MR%20Malkus%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Trump's%20order%2C%20American%20taxpayers%20spent%20nearly%20%24200%20billion%20in%20federal%20funds%20on%20schools%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20%2460%20billion%20already%20allocated%20annually%20for%20federal%20school%20funding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Baltimore%2C%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20high%20schools%20have%20zero%20students%20who%20can%20do%20basic%20mathematics%20-%20not%20even%20the%20very%20simplest%20of%20mathematics.%20They're%20talking%20about%20like%20adding%20a%20few%20numbers%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemocratic%20Backlash%3A%20%26quot%3BSee%20You%20in%20Court%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20executive%20order%20has%20provoked%20an%20immediate%20and%20forceful%20response%20from%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20be%20focused%20on%20helping%20our%20kids%20with%20math%20and%20reading-the%20basics%20they%20need%20to%20succeed.%20Absolutely%20no%20one%20is%20asking%20for%20three%20out-of-touch%20billionaires%20to%20rip%20apart%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20over%20some%20deranged%20far-right%20culture%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Democratic%20Senator%20Patty%20Murray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20taking%20a%20wrecking%20ball%20to%20the%20department%2C%20Trump%20is%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20students%20to%20get%20financial%20aid%2C%20jeopardizing%20the%20funding%20schools%20and%20families%20count%20on%20every%20day%2C%20and%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20predatory%20businesses%20to%20rip%20students%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20you're%20just%20trying%20to%20wear%20us%20out.%20But%20for%20the%20record%2C%20I%20am%20not%20overwhelmed.%20My%20zone%20isn't%20flooded.%20I%20will%20fight%20your%20illegal%20behavior%20until%20the%20cows%20come%20home%2C%20and%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20who've%20contacted%20my%20office%20since%20you%20started%20this%20nonsense%20are%20on%20the%20same%20page%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Democratic%20Senator%20Tina%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSee%20you%20in%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20American%20Federation%20of%20Teachers%20President%20Randi%20Weingarten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ms%20McMahon%20will%20be%20tasked%20with%20dismantling%20the%20agency%2C%20some%20programs%20are%20congressionally%20mandated%20and%20cannot%20be%20abolished%20without%20legislative%20action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20The%20Department%20Do%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20Education%20Department's%20funding%20for%20K-12%20education%20-%20Kindergarten%20through%20Grade%2012%20-%20%C2%A0flows%20through%20Title%20I%2C%20which%20supports%20low-income%20schools%2C%20and%20the%20Individuals%20with%20Disabilities%20Education%20Act%20(IDEA).%20These%20programs%20help%20pay%20for%20special%20education%20services%2C%20additional%20teaching%20positions%2C%20and%20school%20counsellors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20department's%20key%20responsibilities%20is%20managing%20%241.5%20trillion%20in%20student%20loan%20debt%20for%20over%2040%20million%20borrowers.%20It%20also%20administers%20the%20Pell%20Grant%20program%20and%20the%20Free%20Application%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20(FAFSA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20made%20student%20debt%20relief%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20its%20agenda.%20Despite%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20striking%20down%20his%20loan%20cancellation%20plan%2C%20Biden's%20administration%20has%20forgiven%20over%20%24175%20billion%20in%20student%20debt%20for%204.8%20million%20borrowers%20through%20targeted%20programs.%20Trump%20has%20strongly%20criticised%20Biden's%20student%20debt%20relief%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunfair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department's%20Office%20for%20Civil%20Rights%20enforces%20anti-discrimination%20laws%20in%20schools%2C%20investigating%20cases%20related%20to%20race%2C%20gender%2C%20and%20disability%20rights.%20Under%20Biden%2C%20the%20office%20expanded%20protections%20for%20LGBTQ%2B%20students%2C%20issued%20guidance%20on%20racial%20disparities%20in%20discipline%2C%20and%20collected%20data%20on%20educational%20inequities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20administration%20has%20already%20shifted%20priorities.%20The%20US%20President%20has%20pledged%20to%20exclude%20transgender%20students%20from%20Title%20IX%20protections%2C%20a%20crucial%20law%20against%20sex-based%20discrimination%20in%20educational%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Trump%20Shut%20Down%20The%20Department%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo.%20At%20least%20not%20on%20his%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President%20would%20need%20approval%20from%20Congress%20with%20a%20Senate%20majority%20of%20at%20least%2060%20out%20of%20100%20senators.%20Which%20seems%20unlikely%20at%20this%20point%20as%20the%20Republicans%20have%20only%20a%2053-47%20majority%20in%20the%20Senate.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742548680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F6321ql5g_donald-trump-ndtv-_625x300_21_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-explained-inside-donald-trumps-dismantling-of-us-