2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20minds%20behind%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20oldest%20mutual%20funds%20share%20timeless%20investing%20truths%20for%20another%20century%20of%20gains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222049%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Market%20bull%20money%20stocks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7ba756080194819f98b0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221537%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Vanguard%20Wellington%20Fund%2C%20formed%20before%20the%20Great%20Depression%2C%20is%20still%20thriving.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20portfolio%20managers%20shared%20how%20they've%20crushed%20the%20competition%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20how%20the%20team%20picks%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20while%20they're%20still%20big%20believers%20in%20bonds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20healthy%20respect%20for%20history%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20living%20in%20the%20past.%20Nor%20does%20it%20mean%20driving%20a%20car%20by%20only%20looking%20through%20the%20rearview%20mirror.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManagers%20of%20the%20Vanguard%20Wellington%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Ffunds%2Fvanguard-wellington-fund-investor-shares-us9219351023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVWELX%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20oldest%20mutual%20funds%2C%20know%20the%20difference.%20That%20helps%20them%20do%20their%20jobs%20in%20reverence%2C%20but%20not%20deference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoren%20Moran%20and%20Daniel%20Pozen%20are%2C%20metaphorically%2C%20standing%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20giants.%20They're%20entrusted%20with%20running%20the%20third-oldest%20active%20mutual%20fund%3B%20its%20inception%20was%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.vanguard.com%2Finvestment-products%2Fmutual-funds%2Fprofile%2Fvwelx%23overview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuly%201%2C%201929%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20only%20investment%20products%20created%20before%20the%20Great%20Depression%20that's%20still%20standing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Vanguard%20Wellington%20Fund%20%E2%80%94%20named%20for%20the%20second-largest%20asset%20manager%20on%20Earth%20and%20Boston-based%20trillion-dollar%20firm%20Wellington%20%E2%80%94%20is%20far%20from%20a%20relic.%20The%20fund%2C%20which%20has%20over%20%24113%20billion%20in%20assets%2C%20ranks%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8401f9bc2278607961f48d5e521e3679dcef1ca21603c141f4fd615271cdd179%26postID%3D67dc3d5e4e85a4b149909b96%26postSlug%3Dinvesting-strategy-how-to-invest-stocks-fixed-income-vanguard-wellington-2025-3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.morningstar.com%252Ffunds%252Fxnas%252FVWELX%252Fperformance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop%208%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20category%20in%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20per%20Morningstar.%20And%20it's%20only%20finished%20in%20the%20bottom%20half%20of%20its%20peer%20group%20once%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20recently%20spoke%20with%20Moran%20and%20Pozen%20about%20their%20investing%20strategy%2C%20and%20how%20they're%20guiding%20the%20Vanguard%20Wellington%20Fund%20as%20it%20approaches%20its%20100th%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portfolio%20managers%20explained%20that%20their%20fund's%20impressive%20track%20record%20is%20just%20one%20of%20its%20hard-to-match%20advantages.%20Others%20include%20its%20history%2C%20reputation%20and%20brand%2C%20resources%2C%20access%20to%20management%20teams%2C%20size%20%E2%80%94%20which%20lets%20it%20offer%20a%20comically%20low%20expense%20ratio%20of%200.25%25%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20a%20long-term%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20worried%20about%20outperforming%20this%20quarter%20or%20next%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pozen%2C%20who's%20been%20with%20the%20fund%20for%20six%20years.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20concerned%2C%20or%20focused%2C%20on%20delivering%20great%20performance%20over%20the%20long%20term.%20So%20I%20think%20it%20allows%20us%20to%20make%20better%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%20more%20patient%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a43fad7-a31f-4a9c-84a4-912b1146d248%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20stand%20out%20while%20fitting%20in%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vanguard%20Wellington%20Fund%20has%20three%20main%20goals%2C%20explained%20Pozen%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20stock%20part%20of%20the%20portfolio%3A%20outperform%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20over%20time%2C%20offer%20a%20dividend%20yield%20that's%20equal%20or%20greater%20to%20the%20market%2C%20and%20provide%20downside%20protection%20in%20difficult%20market%20and%20economic%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmart%20stock%20selection%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20mission.%20Companies%20that%20create%20economic%20value%20for%20shareholders%2C%20both%20through%20earnings%20and%20dividends%2C%20should%20be%20rewarded%20by%20investors%20over%20time%2C%20Pozen%20said.%20Conversely%2C%20firms%20at%20risk%20of%20getting%20disrupted%20or%20becoming%20obsolete%20are%20unwise%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20focus%20is%20on%20identifying%20companies%20that%20can%20deliver%20value%20creation%20at%20an%20attractive%20rate%20in%20absolute%20and%20higher%20than%20the%20market%20over%20the%20long%20term%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20a%20way%20that's%20reasonably%20predictable%20and%20understandable%2C%20such%20that%20we%20don't%20end%20up%20buying%20high%20and%20selling%20low%2C%26quot%3B%20Pozen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20last%20point%20is%20crucial.%20Pozen%20isn't%20trying%20to%20time%20the%20market%2C%20as%20he%20picks%20stocks%20with%20a%20four-%20to%20five-year%20time%20horizon%20in%20mind%2C%20but%20valuations%20are%20top%20of%20mind.%20Having%20a%20bottom-up%20approach%20means%20there%20isn't%20a%20line%20in%20the%20sand%20based%20on%20a%20certain%20valuation%20metric%20that%20disqualifies%20a%20stock%20from%20consideration%2C%20though%20it's%20prudent%20to%20see%20where%20it%20is%20relative%20to%20the%20market%20and%20its%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20don't%20always%20seem%20to%20care%20about%20valuations%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20how%20the%20market%20rallied%20while%20hovering%20around%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyardeni.com%2Fcharts%2Fstock-market-p-e-ratios%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistorically%20high%20earnings%20multiple%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20when%20there's%20market%20turbulence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-correction-sp500-outlook-trump-trade-war-bear-market-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20there's%20been%20lately%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bprice%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20the%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%20comes%20back%20into%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221984%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20vals%203-20-25%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dc3fc2b8b41a9673fb3aa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221114%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYardeni%20Research%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20careful%20vetting%20of%20companies'%20valuations%20has%20helped%20Pozen%20and%20Moran's%20fund%20hold%20up%20during%20down%20years%2C%20like%202015%2C%202018%2C%20and%202022.%20And%20although%20the%20fund%20has%20struggled%20in%20a%20choppy%202025%2C%20the%20portfolio%20managers%20have%20plenty%20of%20time%20to%20extend%20their%20outperformance%20streak%20to%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20secret%20of%20this%20fund's%20consistent%20performance%20is%20that%20its%20holdings%20are%20benchmark-relative%2C%20meaning%20that%20its%20fate%20is%20tied%2C%20at%20least%20in%20part%2C%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20Its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.vanguard.com%2Finvestment-products%2Fmutual-funds%2Fprofile%2Fvwelx%23portfolio-composition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20largest%20holdings%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20all%20members%20of%20the%20vaunted%20Magnificent%20Seven%2C%20and%20only%20Tesla%20didn't%20crack%20the%20top%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20this%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20that%20Pozen%20is%20excited%20about%20mega-cap%20growth%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20confuse%20their%20large%20absolute%20weight%2C%20necessarily%2C%20with%20our%20positive%20or%20negative%20conviction%20in%20the%20stock%2C%26quot%3B%20Pozen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20unconventional%20approach%20helps%20the%20fund%20stay%20near%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20If%20its%20holdings%20had%20little%20in%20common%20with%20the%20index%2C%20it%20could%20be%20tough%20to%20stay%20within%20striking%20distance.%20It's%20the%20prioritization%20of%20the%20other%2060%20or%20so%20stocks%20that%20determines%20whether%20the%20fund%20meets%20its%20mandate%20of%20outperformance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc413568-40ba-4491-b317-de14c509e8ee%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20the%2060%2F40%20portfolio%20isn't%20dead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20vital%20as%20stock%20selection%20is%2C%20equities%20only%20make%20up%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20this%20mutual%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%2035%25%20of%20invested%20assets%20are%20in%20fixed%20income%2C%20which%20is%20Moran's%20domain.%20That%20smaller%20share%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20an%20afterthought.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20this%20part%20of%20the%20portfolio%20is%20crucial%20to%20diversification%2C%20income%20generation%2C%20and%20differentiation%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20outperformance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20history%20that%20shows%20that%20it%20generally%20does%20provide%20that%20downside%20protection%2C%20and%20then%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20shareholder%20being%20able%20to%20experience%20the%20positive%20long-term%20return%20dynamics%20of%20equities%20in%20a%20lower%20volatility%20context%2C%26quot%3B%20Moran%2C%20who's%20been%20on%20the%20fund%20since%20early%202017%2C%20said%20of%20fixed%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20fixed%20income%2C%20Moran%20also%20follows%20bond%20benchmarks%20and%20keeps%20a%20mix%20of%20US%20Treasuries%20and%20investment-grade%20coupons%20across%20durations.%20The%20typical%20bond%20has%20a%204.9%25%20yield%20to%20maturity%20and%20a%20duration%20of%20just%20under%20seven%20years%2C%20but%20there%20are%20short-%20and%20medium-term%20coupons%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20investors%20have%20moved%20away%20from%20fixed%20income%2C%20which%20has%20woefully%20underperformed%20stocks%20for%20much%20of%20the%2017%20years%20since%20the%20so-called%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis.%20That%20includes%20a%20brutal%202022%2C%20which%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D377b16420eda8e888c280220651035ac38c0f8f7bad55b129fa65b74caef53ec%26postID%3D67dc3d5e4e85a4b149909b96%26postSlug%3Dinvesting-strategy-how-to-invest-stocks-fixed-income-vanguard-wellington-2025-3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.morningstar.com%252Fportfolios%252Fwhy-naysayers-were-wrong-6040-portfolio%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20worst%20years%20ever%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%2060-40%20stock-bond%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2260-40%20decline%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dc3ff963d72727e197c6ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJP%20Morgan%20Asset%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20been%20a%20particularly%20robust%20market%20environment%20since%20the%20GFC%2C%20with%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20short%20interruptions%2C%26quot%3B%20Pozen%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20and%20so%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20to%20forget%20about%20all%20of%20the%20history%20that%20pr