0Judge%2C%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20Shares%20What%20Bothers%20Him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20pertaining%20to%20the%20alleged%20recovery%20of%20cash%20from%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20sitting%20judge%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20was%20raised%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Friday%2C%20with%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20saying%20he%20would%20find%20a%20mechanism%20for%20holding%20a%20structured%20discussion%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaising%20the%20issue%20in%20the%20morning%20session%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20also%20sought%20the%20Chair's%20response%20on%20judicial%20accountability%20and%20reminded%20him%20about%20a%20pending%20notice%20regarding%20the%20impeachment%20of%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20morning%2C%20we%20have%20read%20about%20a%20shocking%20case%20of%20huge%20amounts%20of%20cash%20unearthed%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20earlier%2C%2050%20members%20of%20Parliament%20had%20submitted%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20chairman%20regarding%20certain%20remarks%20that%20were%20made%20by%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20said%20the%20chairman%20himself%20has%20repeatedly%20spoken%20about%20the%20urgency%20for%20judicial%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20Congress%20member%20also%20sought%20to%20remind%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20that%20he%20had%20directed%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20House%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20request%20that%20you%20please%20make%20some%20observations%20on%20this%20and%20give%20necessary%20directions%20to%20the%20government%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20proposal%20for%20increasing%20judicial%20accountability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20related%20to%20the%20alleged%20recovery%20of%