the%20category%20of%20assault%20with%20intent%20to%20disrobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20judgment%2C%20Ms%20Devi%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bwrong%26quot%3B%20and%20urged%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20take%20note%20of%20the%20matter.%20She%20warned%20that%20such%20a%20ruling%20would%20%26quot%3Bsend%20a%20wrong%20message%20to%20society%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20statement%20comes%20in%20response%20to%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20Justice%20Ram%20Manohar%20Narayan%20Mishra%2C%20who%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20two%20men%20who%20had%20challenged%20a%20lower%20court's%20decision%20to%20summon%20them%20under%20charges%20of%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20Ms%20Devi's%20sentiments%2C%20other%20women%20leaders%20also%20called%20for%20Supreme%20Court%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20quite%20disgusting%20the%20way%20there%20is%20a%20complete%20disregard%20of%20women%20by%20and%20large%20in%20the%20country%2C%20which%20we%20need%20to%20get%20over%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20June%20Malia%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20unfortunate.%20I%20am%20very%20shocked%20at%20the%20comments%20made%20in%20the%20judgment.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20shameful%20scenario.%20How%20can%20the%20act%20that%20was%20committed%20by%20those%20men%20can%20not%20be%20taken%20as%20an%20act%20amounting%20to%20rape%3F%20I%20don't%20understand%20the%20logic%20behind%20this%20judgment.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20needs%20to%20step%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Swati%20Maliwal%2C%20former%20DCW%20chief%20and%20AAP%20MP%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20dates%20back%20to%20November%2010%2C%202021.%20According%20to%20the%20complaint%20filed%20by%20the%20victim%2C%20she%20and%20her%2014-year-old%20daughter%20were%20returning%20from%20the%20home%20of%20her%20sister-in-law%20in%20the%20evening%20when%20three%20men%20from%20their%20village%20-%20Pawan%2C%20Akash%2C%20and%20Ashok%20-%20approached%20them%20on%20a%20muddy%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%20offered%20to%20drop%20the%20victim's%20daughter%20home%20on%20his%20motorcycle%2C%20and%20the%20woman%2C%20trusting%20him%2C%20allowed%20her%20daughter%20to%20go%20with%20him.%20The%20accused%20stopped%20on%20the%20way%20and%20allegedly%20assaulted%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20victim's%20complaint%2C%20Pawan%20and%20Akash%20grabbed%20her%20breasts%2C%20and%20Akash%20tried%20to%20drag%20her%20beneath%20a%20culvert.%20He%20also%20broke%20the%20string%20of%20her%20pyjama.%20The%20assault%20was%20interrupted%20when%20two%20people%20arrived%20at%20the%20scene%20after%20hearing%20the%20victim's%20cries%20for%20help.%20The%20accused%20then%20reportedly%20brandished%20a%20country-made%20pistol%20and%20fled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20an%20investigation%2C%20a%20trial%20court%20had%20summoned%20the%20accused%20under%20Section%20376%20of%20the%20IPC%20(rape)%2C%20along%20with%20other%20relevant%20charges.%20The%20accused%20challenged%20this%20order%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mishra%2C%20while%20reviewing%20the%20case%2C%20observed%20that%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20accused%20did%20not%20constitute%20rape%20or%20even%20an%20attempt%20to%20rape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20allegation%20against%20accused%20Pawan%20and%20Akash%20is%20that%20they%20grabbed%20the%20breasts%20of%20the%20victim%20and%20Akash%20tried%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20lower%20garment%20of%20the%20victim%20and%20for%20that%20purpose%2C%20they%20had%20broken%20string%20of%20her%20lower%20garments%20and%20tried%20to%20drag%20her%20beneath%20the%20culvert%2C%20but%20due%20to%20intervention%20of%20witnesses%20they%20left%20the%20victim%20and%20fled%20away%20from%20the%20place%20of%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20fact%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20draw%20an%20inference%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20had%20determined%20to%20commit%20rape%20on%20the%20victim%20as%20apart%20from%20these%20facts%20no%20other%20act%20is%20attributed%20to%20them%20to%20further%20their%20alleged%20desire%20to%20commit%20rape%20on%20the%20victim%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20concluded%20that%20the%20case%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20legal%20threshold%20for%20an%20attempt%20to%20commit%20rape.%20The%20court%20further%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20difference%20between%20preparation%20and%20actual%20attempt%20to%20commit%20an%20offence%20consists%20chiefly%20in%20the%20greater%20degree%20of%20determination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742538840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fq7j85pqg_annpurna-devi-allahabad-high-court-_625x300_21_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrong-judgment-minister-on-not-rape-order-by-allahabad-high-court-judge-7974056%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Annpurna%20Devi%20today%20strongly%20condemned%20a%20recent%20judgment%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20ruled%20that%20the%20act%20of%20grabbing%20a%20woman's%20breast%20and%20snapping%20the%20string%20of%20her%20pyjama%20does%20not%20constitute%20rape.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrong-judgment-minister-on-not-rape-order-by-allahabad-high-court-judge-7974056%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sobhita%20gives%20a%20sarcastic%20reply%20as%20Naga%20takes%20a%20jibe%20at%20her%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742538749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119289502%2Cimgsize-51232.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsobhita-dhulipala-has-a-sarcastic-reply-as-naga-chaitanya-takes-a-jibe-at-her-these-a