igns%20of%20fertility%20and%20symbols%20of%20divine%20protection%2C%20Bhutan's%20priapic%20obsession%20transcends%20anatomy%20and%20is%20anchored%20in%20spirituality.%20The%2015th-century%20Buddhist%20saint%2C%20Drukpa%20Kunley%E2%80%94affectionately%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BDivine%20Madman%26quot%3B%E2%80%94championed%20these%20symbols%2C%20enmeshing%20eroticism%20with%20enlightenment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karma%20Choden's%20%3Cem%3EPhallus%3A%20Crazy%20Wisdom%20from%20Bhutan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Marc%20Domsky's%20photographic%20journey%2C%20%3Cem%3EPhallus%20Through%20Bhutan%3A%20Journey%20of%20the%20Magic%20Thunderbolt%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20read%E2%80%94along%20with%20some%20far-out%20visual%20evidence%E2%80%94how%20they%20are%20talismans%20against%20malevolence%2C%20markers%20of%20prosperity%2C%20boons%20for%20progeny%2C%20reflecting%20a%20culture%20where%20the%20sacred%20and%20sacrilegious%20integrate%20fearlessly.%20I%20got%20a%20large%20wooden%20one%20for%20an%20aunty%20of%20mine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20Move%20Is%20To%20Risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20drive%20out%20to%20Punakha%2C%20the%20neck%20remains%20in%20agony.%20Mentally%2C%20I%20take%20stock%20of%20other%20writers%20who%20endured%20far%20worse%20fates%20on%20the%20road.%20Bruce%20Chatwin%2C%20fevered%20and%20frail%20in%20Patagonia%2C%20his%20body%20betraying%20him%20even%20as%20the%20landscape%20turned%20into%20his%20muse.%20Bill%20Bryson%2C%20sun-scorched%20in%20Australia%2C%20learned%20how%20heat%20tasers%20humour%20to%20stoicism.%20And%20Rolf%20Potts%2C%20wandering%20through%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20saw%20in%20food%20poisoning%20not%20an%20enemy%20but%20an%20initiation%E2%80%94diarrhoea%20as%20portal%20to%20enlightenment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20move%20is%20to%20risk%3B%20all%20risk%20entails%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20