0said%20in%20the%20nearly%20two-minute%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20historic%20day%20for%20Indian%20federalism!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20extend%20my%20warmest%20welcome%20to%20the%20leaders%20from%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Odisha%2C%20West%20Bengal%20%26amp%3B%20Punjab%20who%20are%20joining%20us%20for%20the%20Joint%20Action%20Committee%20meeting%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FFairDelimitation%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23FairDelimitation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20All-Party%20Meeting%20on%20March%205%20was%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FWra2NmccIA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FWra2NmccIA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20M.K.Stalin%20(%40mkstalin)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmkstalin%2Fstatus%2F1902924627162144794%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2021%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(the%20proposed%20delimitation)%20strikes%20at%20the%20very%20foundation%20of%20federalism%20in%20India.%20It%20will%20erode%20the%20essence%20of%20democracy%20itself.%20Our%20voices%20in%20Parliament%20will%20be%20silenced.%20Our%20rights%20will%20be%20compromised.%20This%20is%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20undermine%20certain%20states...%20states%20that%20have%20controlled%20population%20growth%2C%20governed%20efficiently%2C%20and%20contributed%20to%20national%20progress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20has%20vociferously%20opposed%20the%20centre's%20plans%20for%20a%20delimitation%20based%20on%20current%20population%20levels%2C%20arguing%20it%20will%20penalise%20states%20that%20have%20successfully%20controlled%20population%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-