system%2C%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20NPCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Banks%20Will%20Implement%20The%20New%20Rule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBanks%20and%20PSPs%20will%20periodically%20flag%20and%20remove%20inactive%2C%20reassigned%2C%20or%20deactivated%20mobile%20numbers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAffected%20users%20will%20receive%20notifications%20before%20their%20UPI%20services%20are%20suspended.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20a%20mobile%20number%20remains%20inactive%20despite%20warnings%2C%20it%20will%20be%20delisted%20from%20UPI%20to%20prevent%20fraud.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20can%20restore%20their%20UPI%20access%20by%20updating%20their%20mobile%20number%20before%20the%20deadline.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Will%20Be%20Affected%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20who%20changed%20their%20mobile%20number%20but%20didn't%20update%20it%20with%20their%20bank.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20with%20inactive%20numbers%20that%20haven't%20been%20used%20for%20calls%2C%20SMS%2C%20or%20banking%20alerts%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20who%20surrendered%20their%20number%20without%20updating%20their%20bank%20details.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20whose%20old%20number%20was%20reassigned%20to%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20To%20Keep%20Your%20UPI%20Active%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECheck%20if%20your%20mobile%20number%20is%20active%20by%20calling%20or%20messaging%20someone.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEnsure%20you%20receive%20SMS%20alerts%20and%20OTPs%20from%20your%20bank.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUpdate%20your%20UPI-linked%20mobile%20number%20via%20net%20banking%2C%20UPI%20apps%2C%20ATMs%2C%20or%20by%20visiting%20your%20bank%20branch.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20A%20Mobile%20Number%20Is%20Important%20For%20UPI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYour%20mobile%20number%20is%20linked%20to%20your%20bank%20f